1.What is Unity Catalog and why was it introduced?

Answer: Unity Catalog is Databricks' centralized governance solution that provides:
Unified access control
Data discovery
Lineage
Auditing
Data sharing
across all Databricks workspaces and clouds.

Before Unity Catalog:
Permissions were managed at workspace level.
Metastore was workspace-specific.
Governance was difficult across multiple workspaces.

Unity Catalog creates a centralized governance layer.

